name: Safavieh_Metro_Clay_Leather_Side_Chairs_(Set_of_2)
reviews: I was so happy with these chairs...a tad darker than my screen shows but actually more like I was looking for. The size is great, made for adults! Can't wait to get them to our new house and with my new table!
I purchase these chair for my dining room and everyone loves them as much as I do.
I am very pleased. Love the color.
Love these chairs. Ordered four and loved them , so I ordered two more. Style, quality was more than I expected when I received them. They look great with the table I purchased.
The chairs are exactly what I wanted. I just love them.
description:
Simplicity and elegance combine in this stylish leather dining
chair set. Each of the two chairs is created using birch wood and
leather, and the exposed nail heads add extra interest and a touch
of contemporary flair. Slightly tapered backrests and cushioned
surfaces make the chairs a comfortable place to enjoy a meal.
